caption:
My ritual wont work for you, and you shouldn’t want it to.

It’s important to remember the intention behind everything we let into our routines and inner world.

✨ What makes you energised?
✨ What makes you feel ready to take on the day?
✨ What keeps you going?

The intention behind the ritual is just as important as the ritual itself.

you can’t have one without the other.
